00:00:36,114 --> 00:00:37,255
[SPEAKER_04]: Rome to Hong Kong.

3
00:00:37,735 --> 00:00:44,017
[SPEAKER_04]: But I hope we can do something like this in Africa sometime soon because the same is true.

