7
00:01:15,491 --> 00:01:32,906
[SPEAKER_04]: I think it can be even higher than that, up to 10% per year, based on a strategy of strong economic, financial, and monetary integration in Africa, and strong connections of Africa

8
00:01:33,450 --> 00:01:38,494
[SPEAKER_04]: with all of the major parts of the world economy.

9
00:01:39,395 --> 00:01:51,425
[SPEAKER_04]: So I think everything we do could be organized around a very high-ambition growth strategy for Africa.

10
00:01:52,325 --> 00:02:02,634
[SPEAKER_04]: There's just a lot of potential headroom for rapid growth by building the core infrastructure

11
00:02:03,406 --> 00:02:16,350
[SPEAKER_04]: and by upgrading and universalizing education at all levels and the science and technology innovation agenda for Africa.

12
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:23,472
