107
00:17:27,537 --> 00:17:36,462
[SPEAKER_04]: So I think that you can find partners for long-term financing for building out this continental scale program.

108
00:17:37,082 --> 00:17:39,663
[SPEAKER_04]: I'll stop there and turn it back over to you, Kevin.

109
00:17:40,064 --> 00:17:46,127
[SPEAKER_04]: But just to say, we need to aim for a high growth scenario.

110
00:17:46,747 --> 00:17:58,954
[SPEAKER_04]: And we need to build the underlying continental scale institutions and the physical infrastructure and the human capital to make that happen.

111
00:17:59,654 --> 00:18:06,398
[SPEAKER_04]: And the wonderful volume, Kevin, that you organized for the African Development Bank spells that out.

112
00:18:06,958 --> 00:18:12,422
[SPEAKER_04]: in detail as a very realistic, high-ambition approach.

113
00:18:12,862 --> 00:18:18,506
[SPEAKER_04]: And that's the one that I think Africa certainly should follow and that will be a success.

114
00:18:19,106 --> 00:18:21,888
[SPEAKER_04]: So let me pause there and turn it back over to you.

115
00:18:23,089 --> 00:18:28,253
[SPEAKER_02]: Thank you very much, Jeff, for that very interesting intervention.

116
00:18:29,053 --> 00:18:32,055
