126
00:20:00,803 --> 00:20:06,966
[SPEAKER_02]: Tax reforms to raise revenues domestically, and we heard from my presentation

127
00:20:07,550 --> 00:20:11,352
[SPEAKER_02]: over 780 billion dollars waiting for us there.

128
00:20:13,013 --> 00:20:19,477
[SPEAKER_02]: Mining contracts, he also talks about how to structure that so that we can track more.

129
00:20:22,339 --> 00:20:25,941
This thing is not working.

