00:20:26,041 --> 00:20:34,106
[SPEAKER_02]: Okay, so that we can get more

131
00:20:35,242 --> 00:20:42,368
[SPEAKER_02]: really is from what we have the most, what I refer to as sitting on gold and begging for resources.

132
00:20:43,028 --> 00:20:45,030
[SPEAKER_02]: But Jeff, I would even go a bit further.

133
00:20:45,050 --> 00:20:51,976
[SPEAKER_02]: The Minerals Critical Minerals Conference hosted by President C.J.

134
00:20:52,136 --> 00:21:03,926
[SPEAKER_02]: Ota just yesterday, I was asking the mining ministers for mining and minerals, why we are actually mining these agreements instead of

135
00:21:04,466 --> 00:21:06,086
