136
00:21:08,427 --> 00:21:29,033
[SPEAKER_02]: Because for sustainable development, it doesn't make sense to ship heavy metals thousands of miles away and produce batteries, and by the thought of lithium ion battery minerals, ship them to US, China, produce batteries and bring them back.

