00:22:06,620 --> 00:22:08,502
[SPEAKER_02]: Financial and monetary integration.

144
00:22:09,023 --> 00:22:11,965
[SPEAKER_02]: Again, a broad point that Jeff raises for us.

145
00:22:12,506 --> 00:22:14,067
[SPEAKER_02]: He says Africa needs this.

146
00:22:15,068 --> 00:22:16,830
[SPEAKER_02]: And Africa knows that it needs it.

147
00:22:17,050 --> 00:22:27,719
[SPEAKER_02]: And that is why the African Monetary Institute, I think I mentioned it in my presentation as well, which takes us towards that African Central Bank.

